@startuml
[*] --> CreateAccount
CreateAccount --> Login : create account and log in
Login --> ApplyForVisa : apply for visa after logging in
ApplyForVisa --> PaymentMade : make payment
PaymentMade --> ApplicationAccepted : application accepted
ApplicationAccepted --> ViewStatus : view status
ViewStatus --> CheckStatus : check status
CheckStatus --> CancelApplication : cancel application
CancelApplication --> Logout : log out
Login --> ModifyDetails : modify details after logging in
ModifyDetails --> Logout : log out
Login --> ViewDetails : view details after logging in
ViewDetails --> Logout : log out
Login --> ViewPurpose : view purpose of application after logging in
ViewPurpose --> StatusUpdated : status updated
StatusUpdated --> GiveFeedback : give feedback
GiveFeedback --> Logout : log out
ApplyForVisa --> DocumentCheck : document check
DocumentCheck --> ApprovedOrRejected : visa approved or rejected
ApprovedOrRejected --> StatusUpdated : status updated

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
state "Log In" as Login
state "Apply For Visa" as ApplyForVisa
state "Payment Made" as PaymentMade
state "Application Accepted" as ApplicationAccepted
state "View Status" as ViewStatus
state "Check Status" as CheckStatus
state "Cancel Application" as CancelApplication
state "Modify Details" as ModifyDetails
state "View Details" as ViewDetails
state "View Purpose" as ViewPurpose
state "Approved Or Rejected" as ApprovedOrRejected
state "Status Updated" as StatusUpdated
state "Give Feedback" as GiveFeedback

note right of Login : user must be logged in to perform actions
@enduml
